magazine/.highlight/israeli-peace-activists-who-lost-loved-ones-in-the-hamas-massacre-stand-their-ground/0000018b-7235-d51e-a3cb-737d82d80000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯正在加沙的地堡中重新调整中东的力量平衡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/from-its-bunkers-in-gaza-hamas-is-rejiggering-the-balance-of-power-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-71a6-dec3-a59f-f5f7c1a30000</link><description>哈马斯的袭击迫使卡塔尔、沙特阿拉伯、埃及、土耳其和阿拉伯联合酋长国组成了一个不稳定的联盟。目前尚不清楚他们中的任何人是否能够拆除目前在加沙的炸弹</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 19:18:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/from-its-bunkers-in-gaza-hamas-is-rejiggering-the-balance-of-power-in-the-middle-east/0000018b-71a6-dec3-a59f-f5f7c1a30000</guid></item><item><title>拜登纪念生命之树枪击事件五周年，援引以色列哈马斯大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/biden-marks-fifth-anniversary-of-tree-of-life-shooting-invokes-hamas-massacre-in-israel/0000018b-71eb-dec3-a59f-f5fb90f60000</link><description>拜登在纪念匹兹堡被白人民族主义者杀害的 11 名犹太人时表示，“纪念活动是在大屠杀以来对犹太人来说最致命的一天之后进行的”</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 18:45:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/biden-marks-fifth-anniversary-of-tree-of-life-shooting-invokes-hamas-massacre-in-israel/0000018b-71eb-dec3-a59f-f5fb90f60000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日，以色列国家安全的拐点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/october-7-an-inflection-point-for-israels-national-security/0000018b-7130-d51e-a3cb-717c88f30000</link><description>哈马斯从加沙发起的进攻挑战了以色列所珍视的国防、外交政策和整个地缘政治背景的信条。以色列与伊朗的间接战争只是其后果之一</description><pubDate>Fri, 27 Oct 2023 15:40:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-27/ty-article/.premium/october-7-an-inflection-point-for-israels-national-security/0000018b-7130-d51e-a3cb-717c88f30000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯官员告诉俄罗斯官方媒体，哈马斯将所有人质视为以色列人</title><link>